<div id="chapterTitleBox"><span class="chapterTitle">Chapter 9: Chemical Senses: Olfaction and Gustation</span>
  <p class="pageNumberAuthorName"><a name="content" id="content"></a>Max O. Hutchins, Ph.D., Department of Integrative Biology and Pharmacology, McGovern Medical School<br />
    <br />
    Reviewed and revised 07 Oct 2020</br>
  <hr />
  
